# Lotteries - Money Laundering and Terrorist Financing Risk Assessment 2023

**Overall Risk Rating:** Low (All lottery sectors)

## Summary

The lottery sector, encompassing society lotteries, external lottery managers (ELMs), and the National Lottery, is rated as low risk for money laundering and terrorist financing. The low stake, low prize nature of most lottery products, combined with the high visibility and regulatory oversight, makes lotteries generally unattractive to money launderers.

---

## Society Lotteries and External Lottery Managers

**Overall Risk Rating:** Low

### Inherent Risks by Vulnerability Category

#### Operator Control Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|
| Operators failing to comply with prevention of money laundering and terrorist financing legislation and guidance | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | Decrease in likelihood |
| Third party business relationships and business investors | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |
| Licensee failing to transfer lottery proceeds to charities | Low (1) | Medium (2) | Low (2) | Increase in impact |

#### Licensing and Integrity Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|
| Operator being acquired by organised crime to launder criminal funds | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |

#### Customer Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|
| Anonymous customers (Non-Remote) | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |
| False and stolen identity documentation | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |
| Customer not physically present (remote) | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |

#### Product Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|
| Interactive instant win games (online) | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |
| Scratch cards or interactive instant win games | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |

#### Means of Payment Vulnerabilities

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Overall Risk | Change in Risk |
|------|------------|--------|--------------|----------------|
| Cash transactions (non-remote only) | Low (1) | Low (1) | Low (1) | No change |

